       <p class="scripture-ref">‚Äî Romans 15:13, King James Version (KJV)</p><a href="https://www.biblegateway.com/passage/?search=Romans+15:13&amp;version=KJV" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bible-link">Read Full Chapter ‚Üí</a>
